New The Texas Redistricting Map is here.

It eliminates 5 Democrats Seats:
🔵 9th Green.
🔵 28th Cuellar.
🔵 29th Garcia.
🔵 32nd Johnson.
🔵 34th Gonzalez.

The districts are now Republican:
🔴 9th R+15.2 .
🔴 28th R+10.4 .
🔴 29th R+17.7 .
🔴 32nd R+10.1 .
🔴 34th R+10.3 .  — The Donald
article_summary: Texas Redistricting Map unveiled, eliminating 5 Democratic seats and shifting the balance to 30 Republican districts and 8 Democratic ones. The change has sparked debate among users, with some advocating for further Republican gains and others questioning the feasibility of achieving a 56-42 split.</s>
